# README Footer

Every **`README.md`** in this repository (root, `packages/**`, `.cursor/plans/**`, etc.) must end with this footer:

```markdown
---

#Col3:23
```

- Put the footer after the last section; one blank line before `---` is fine.
- Do not add text after `#Col3:23`.
- When creating a new README or editing one, keep or add this footer.
- Run `npm run format:check` (Prettier) on touched README files.
